{"article_id":"Aq4TkpMrRKh4ikJk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Disgraced former Gov . Mark Sanford overcame past scandals","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to win House seat","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Sanford is a veteran campaigner","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"while opponent Colbert Bush made some rookie mistakes","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Mark Sanford is heading back to Washington after detours along the Appalachian Trail and Argentina .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"The former South Carolina governor finished his second term in office three years ago with his political career dead in the water thanks to a well-publicized extra-marital affair and ethics violations .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"But he came away Tuesday with a victory over Democratic opponent Elizabeth Colbert Busch in the special election for a vacant House seat in the Palmetto State 's 1st Congressional District","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"-- the same seat","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he once held .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Here 's what we 've learned ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"or better yet , re-learned , from Sanford 's victory","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"From the start of his bid for Congress , Sanford was very open on the campaign trail about the affair","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and made it the subject of his first TV ad .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Sanford asked for ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and received ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"political redemption from the voters .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"JUST WATCHED Sanford 's stunning political comeback","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"MUST WATCH Sanford 's stunning political comeback 02:49","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Mark Sanford wins a second chance","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"Mark Sanford wins a second chance","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"02:29","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"`` I want to acknowledge a God not just of second chances but third , fourth , fifth , sixth , seventh , eighth chances ,","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"because that is the reality of our shared humanity , ''","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"said Sanford at his victory celebration Tuesday night .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"`` I am one imperfect man","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"saved by God 's grace . ''","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"He repeated that theme minutes later at a news conference with reporters .","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"`` I think","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"we 're always on the search for redemption","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"and I think","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"this is certainly a degree of political redemption . ''","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"Colbert Busch 's campaign , as well as two national Democratic groups","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"which contributed money and support to her campaign ,","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"highlighted the affair .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"At their only general election debate , Colbert Busch confronted Sanford about his 2009 secret trip to Argentina","depth":15},{"id":40,"text":"to see his mistress .","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"And her campaign went up with a TV commercial","depth":16},{"id":42,"text":"which slammed Sanford for using `` tax dollars","depth":18},{"id":43,"text":"to visit his mistress in Argentina ,","depth":18},{"id":44,"text":"disappeared for a week","depth":19},{"id":45,"text":"leaving no one in charge ,","depth":19},{"id":46,"text":"betrayed all","depth":20},{"id":47,"text":"who trusted him ,","depth":20},{"id":48,"text":"then lied","depth":20},{"id":49,"text":"to cover it up .","depth":20},{"id":50,"text":"Mark Sanford , it 's a question of character . ''","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"The Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee and the pro-Democrat House Majority PAC ,","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"which , combined , spent nearly $ 900,000","depth":16},{"id":53,"text":"to try and defeat Sanford ,","depth":16},{"id":54,"text":"also spotlighted the affair in their final ads .","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"For all his political baggage , Mark Sanford is a veteran on the campaign trail .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"And Elizabeth Colbert Busch showed her campaign inexperience at times .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"`` Sanford may be a flawed candidate","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"but he 's a fabulous campaigner , ''","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"said Republican strategist Hogan Gidley , a former executive director of the South Carolina Republican Party .","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"`` Forget the rhetoric or the policy or the delivery","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"-- hand-to-hand , eye-to-eye he 's very good","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"and it 's impossible to outwork him . ''","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"Sanford also seemed to win this election one voter at a time .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"The candidate appeared to be everywhere in the campaign 's closing days .","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"He held nearly 15 events on Monday , with another 10 on Election Day .","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"We knew","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"Democratic voters were fired up ,","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"but the big question concerned Republican voters in a district","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"that the GOP has held for more 30 years .","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"Would they vote even with their reservations about Sanford ?","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"It was a high turnout for a special election .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"Roughly a quarter of the 18-plus population voted , more than 140,000 votes total ,","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"according to a CNN analysis of the vote .","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"`` That seems to have helped Sanford , ''","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"CNN Polling Director Keating Holland said .","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"`` Low turnout would have meant a lot of Republicans","depth":16},{"id":77,"text":"who were reluctant to vote for him","depth":17},{"id":78,"text":"and would n't vote for a Democrat .","depth":17},{"id":79,"text":"High turnout turns that around :","depth":16},{"id":80,"text":"Plenty of Republicans","depth":18},{"id":81,"text":"who had misgivings about Sanford","depth":18},{"id":82,"text":"came out to vote anyway . ''","depth":17},{"id":83,"text":"And House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi might be one reason why .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"Sanford and his campaign repeatedly tied Colbert Busch to Pelosi ,","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"saying","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"that a vote for Colbert Busch would also be a vote for Pelosi ,","depth":17},{"id":87,"text":"who has high negatives with Republican voters","depth":18},{"id":88,"text":"and who most likely would become House speaker again","depth":19},{"id":89,"text":"if the Democrats run the table","depth":20},{"id":90,"text":"and regain control of the chamber in next year 's midterm elections .","depth":20},{"id":91,"text":"`` I 've fought hard over the years","depth":19},{"id":92,"text":"to make South Carolina a better place","depth":20},{"id":93,"text":"to call home .","depth":20},{"id":94,"text":"But those efforts pale now against the larger battle for the direction of our country .","depth":18},{"id":95,"text":"Maybe that 's why Nancy Pelosi and allies have spent more than a million dollars","depth":18},{"id":96,"text":"to defeat me .","depth":18},{"id":97,"text":"But this contest is bigger than them or me ,","depth":17},{"id":98,"text":"it 's about two different visions","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"of how we restore America","depth":19},{"id":100,"text":"and reign in Washington spending , ''","depth":19},{"id":101,"text":"Sanford said ,","depth":16},{"id":102,"text":"looking into the camera in a TV spot","depth":17},{"id":103,"text":"that started running district-wide last week .","depth":17},{"id":104,"text":"Two weeks ago he even debated a cardboard cutout of Pelosi","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"to call out Colbert Busch","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"for not accepting more than one debate .","depth":16},{"id":107,"text":"Macro :","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"The 1st Congressional District is GOP country .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Mitt Romney carried the district by 18 percentage points in last November 's presidential election .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"And Rep. Tim Scott was reelected by 27 points","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"before he was picked by GOP Gov . Nikki Haley","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"to fill the Senate seat","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"vacated by Sen. Jim DeMint ,","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"who stepped down","depth":16},{"id":115,"text":"to take over as the head of the conservative Heritage Foundation .","depth":16},{"id":116,"text":"Even a candidate with serious political baggage like Sanford was able to win .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"Micro :","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Sanford won all five counties in the district .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"He won big","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"where he needed to ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"in the conservative counties of Berkeley and Dorchester ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"taking around 60 % of the vote .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"He carried the district 's second most populous county , Beaufort , by 6 percentage points .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Some Democrats hoped","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"that older voters in that county ,","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"which includes Hilton Head ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"would be turned off by Sanford 's affair .","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"Sanford narrowly carried his home base of Charleston County ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"where the most voters were at stake .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"That was also Colbert Busch 's best hope .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Colbert Busch 's campaign outspent Sanford 's operation in the closing weeks .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"And the DCCC and House Majority PAC combined spent around $ 900,000","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"to try to defeat Sanford ,","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"who received far less support from outside groups .","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"Money matters in campaign politics ,","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"but it 's just one factor","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"in determining a race .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":275,"left":0,"right":274,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":274,"left":142,"right":273,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":139,"right":140,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":145,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":144,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":7,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":269,"right":271,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":146,"right":268,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":240,"right":267,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":240,"left":150,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":152,"right":238,"relation":"j